# Chat Management

## 1. Get All Chats

**Endpoint:** `GET /admin/chats`

**Description:** Get paginated chat history for admin dashboard

**Request Headers:**
```
Authorization: Bearer {access_token}
```

**Query Parameters:**
| Parameter | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-----------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| limit | integer | No | 20 | Number of records per page (1-999) |
| offset | integer | No | 0 | Pagination offset (must be ≥ 0) |
| user_id | string | No | null | Filter by exact user ID |
| search_user_id | string | No | null | Search for user IDs (case-insensitive pattern matching) |

**Success Response (200):**
```json
{
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "chat-123",
      "user_id": "user@example.com",
      "message": "Hello, how are you?",
      "role": "user",
      "timestamp": "2026-04-29T10:30:00Z",
      "total_tokens": 150,
      "cost": 0.0015
    },
    {
      "id": "chat-124",
      "user_id": "user@example.com",
      "message": "I'm doing great!",
      "role": "assistant",
      "timestamp": "2026-04-29T10:30:05Z",
      "total_tokens": 200,
      "cost": 0.002
    }
  ],
  "limit": 20,
  "offset": 0,
  "total": 150,
  "page_count": 2,
  "has_more": true
}
```

**Example Request:**
```
GET /admin/chats?limit=20&offset=0
GET /admin/chats?limit=20&offset=0&user_id=user123
GET /admin/chats?limit=20&offset=0&search_user_id=user
```

