# Facebook Comments Management

## 1. Get All FB Comments

**Endpoint:** `GET /admin/fb-comments`

**Description:** Get Facebook comments with advanced filtering options

**Request Headers:**
```
Authorization: Bearer {access_token}
```

**Query Parameters:**
| Parameter | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-----------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| limit | integer | No | 20 | Number of records per page |
| offset | integer | No | 0 | Pagination offset |
| confidence_bucket | string | No | null | Filter: "low", "medium", or "high" |
| min_confidence | float | No | null | Minimum confidence (0-1) |
| max_confidence | float | No | null | Maximum confidence (0-1) |
| status | string | No | null | Filter by status |
| include_deleted | boolean | No | false | Include deleted comments |
| search_query | string | No | null | Search in comment text |
| start_date | string | No | null | Start date for filtering (ISO format) |
| end_date | string | No | null | End date for filtering (ISO format) |
| read_status | string | No | null | Filter: "read" or "unread" |

**Validation Rules:**
- `confidence_bucket` must be one of: low, medium, high
- `min_confidence` must be ≤ `max_confidence`
- `start_date` must be ≤ `end_date`
- `read_status` must be "read" or "unread"

**Success Response (200):**
```json
{
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "comment-1",
      "comment_id": "fb_123456",
      "comment_text": "Is this service available?",
      "post_id": "post_789",
      "bot_response": "Yes, the service is available 24/7",
      "confidence_score": 0.95,
      "status": "responded",
      "is_read": true,
      "read_by": "admin@example.com",
      "read_at": "2026-04-29T10:00:00Z",
      "created_at": "2026-04-29T09:30:00Z",
      "reply_comment_id": "reply_456",
      "is_deleted": false
    }
  ],
  "limit": 20,
  "offset": 0,
  "total": 156,
  "page_count": 8,
  "has_more": true
}
```

**Response Fields:**
| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| id | string | Database record ID |
| comment_id | string | Facebook comment ID |
| comment_text | string | Original comment text |
| post_id | string | Facebook post ID |
| bot_response | string | Bot's response to comment |
| confidence_score | float | Confidence of bot response (0-1) |
| status | string | Comment status (e.g., "responded", "pending") |
| is_read | boolean | Has admin read this comment? |
| read_by | string | Admin email who read it |
| read_at | string | When admin read it |
| created_at | string | When comment was created |
| reply_comment_id | string | ID of bot's reply comment |
| is_deleted | boolean | Is comment deleted? |

**Example Requests:**
```
GET /admin/fb-comments?limit=20&offset=0
GET /admin/fb-comments?limit=20&offset=0&confidence_bucket=high
GET /admin/fb-comments?limit=20&offset=0&read_status=unread
GET /admin/fb-comments?limit=20&offset=0&min_confidence=0.8&max_confidence=1.0
GET /admin/fb-comments?limit=20&offset=0&search_query=pricing
GET /admin/fb-comments?limit=20&offset=0&start_date=2026-04-01&end_date=2026-04-29
```

