## Pagination Guidelines

For all paginated endpoints:
- Default limit: 20
- Default offset: 0
- Response includes: `limit`, `offset`, `total`, `page_count`, `has_more`

**Example pagination:**
```
GET /admin/chats?limit=20&offset=0      # Page 1 (items 1-20)
GET /admin/chats?limit=20&offset=20     # Page 2 (items 21-40)
GET /admin/chats?limit=20&offset=40     # Page 3 (items 41-60)
```

---

## Rate Limiting

All endpoints are rate-limited to prevent abuse. Headers in response:
```
X-RateLimit-Limit: 100
X-RateLimit-Remaining: 95
X-RateLimit-Reset: 1609459200
```

